{"tid":2124071,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"［有圖警告］我只高腳蛛少左只腳","createTime":"2020-07-25T06:32:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-26T05:42:15.000Z","uid":242102,"like":4,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"665a235fb9640a3aae0435d96494d3867eb9cdfe","tid":2124071,"uid":242102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T06:32:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有蜘蛛圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n警告<br />\n恐懼請左上角<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8H7xsZm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8H7xsZm.jpg&h=bf0380b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aGvWacH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaGvWacH.jpg&h=bfd3aab0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔是特登養<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過聽講係好鄰居<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n容許佢同四腳爬爬在我家共同生活<br />\n（屌d爬爬宜家氾濫多到我要好小心開門關門行路避開佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n但點解左邊得兩隻腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b1c62a66338fdd38463cb533101e786b82c3164","tid":2124071,"uid":242102,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T06:34:03.000Z","msg":"點解得兩隻腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我上網check左邊應該有3隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n是咪唔小心俾我踩斷左隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{